## v2.1.0 (2026-03-30)

**Changed by:** E2E pipeline CI fixes across 5 repos (Agamemnon#3, Nestor#1, Hermes#59, Myrmidons#60, Odysseus#68)
**Verification:** verified-local (CI re-runs pending)

### What changed
- Added 8 new Failed Attempts for C++20/CMake CI patterns
- New patterns: library main() vs GTest conflict, missing CMake test presets, clang-format scope, pixi just dependency, pixi lockfile staleness, claude-review.yml removal, superseded PR handling

### Why
Fixing CI across 5 repos for the E2E pipeline revealed C++20-specific CI failure patterns not covered by v2.0.0 (which focused on Python/Mojo repos). The library main() conflict is particularly subtle — GTest silently doesn't run.

---

